## R117 — SSOT Header Obrigatorio (H/C/S/U)
Toda resposta DEVE incluir o header de status de 20 linhas:
```
NC-SSOT | <timestamp> | <lobes> lobes <doms> dom | <total> rules H:<h> C:<c> S:<s> U:<u> | STEP0:ON | GW:<gw>/<tools> RUFF:<ruff>% | MCP:<status> MC:<mc> OLL:<ollama> | sess:<n> turns:<t> hf:<hf> | EXE:<eng> LEG:<norms> JUD:<courts> FED:pacto SEM:<lobes> RTR:FR-165 | RAC:ON 3W:ON KISS:ON CLAIM:ON
```
- **H**: CentralWatcher `validate_ssot_header()` — bloqueia resposta sem header
- **C**: PulseScheduler audita headers a cada 300s
- **S**: FR-163 SSOT Reporter gera header dinamico
- **U**: T0 revisa no chat

